OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain or
OL,6,Fshowers, locally heavy, gradually
OL,7,Fclearing eastward this evening.
OL,8,FBecoming largely dry with clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping during the second half of
OL,10,Fthe night. Strong winds easing but a
OL,11,Ffurther risk of coastal gales across
OL,12,FKent and Sussex at first.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FVariable amounts of could but
OL,15,Fa widely dry, bright and warm day.
OL,16,FRather breezy during the afternoon,
OL,17,Falthough the winds not as strong
OL,18,Fcompared to Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
